Tool to clear siteid and folderid attributes from inline relationships inside the contents.
Instructions to run the tool.
Stop the Rhythmyx server
Make a back up of your database.
Extract the contents of RhythmyxInlineLinkClearAttribs zip file to InlineLinkClearAttribs folder.
Open InlineLinkClearAttribs.properties file and change the properties to point to your installation.
Start the Rhythmyx server.
Save the file.
Make sure to check-in all the items for the site you are running this tool.
Run the tool by executing RhythmyxInlineLinkClearAttribs.bat file.
The tool removes the site id and folder id properties from the inline relationships.


